    "1. Click Runtime → Change runtime type → Select GPU\n",
    "2. Run all cells (Runtime → Run all)\n",
    "3. Wait for training to complete (~20-30 minutes per stock)\n",
    "4. Download trained models from Google Drive or as ZIP file"
   ]
